programme.title: That ingredient sneaky dog food makers don't want you to know about
programme.desc:
Want less poop, and more dazzling performance from your hunting dog?
Generally, less poop means your dog food contains the highest-quality protein and his body is utilizing almost all of it.
But crafty dog food makers often hide the key ingredient ... the one that will tell ALL about the quality of the protein in your hunting dog's food. And it's the easiest way to tell how good your dog food is.
This ingredient is seldom on the label. You'll have to quit browsing puppy pictures on the Internet and go to the dog food maker's website. If you want more of his food fueling peak performance and less piling up in the yard, it's worth the effort.
